cat << EOF
TightVNC is an enhanced version of VNC which is optimized to work over
slow network connections such as low-speed modem links.  Besides
bandwidth optimizations, TightVNC also includes many other improvements,
optimizations, and bugfixes over VNC.  TightVNC is fully compatible with
the standard VNC.
EOF
